reviews.text: Nice hotel outside of the city with a slightly different feel to the rest of Hong Kong. They offer themed rooms which is great for a kids bday celebration. Nice playroom but only offer 1 hour free session per day. Buffet is good but can get very busy so book early during peak periods. Pool is nice with outdoor water play area. The hotel grounds and gardens are well kept and nice to walk around!

The place is excellent. The only problem is getting a room at a good price. You have to shop when they have a sale. Try to book a room when they're having a sale. I guess it depends on what time of year you're going to be there. But you'll have a good time at this hotel. There's a nice Shopping Plaza near the hotel about a 8 minute walk. They have McDonald's and a bunch of other restaurants and a 7-Eleven at the plaza. Also the bus stop is not too far away. And I have taxis waiting in the lobby if you need that. But I prefer bus and Subway to get around Hong Kong.

Pretty quiet during weekdays. Good for a short get away. Decent rooms with good view. Right next to a nice beach. Can take bus here. If you insist on driving, there is a big public metered parking lot just in front of hotel entrance if you don't want to use the hotel's expensive valet service.

We booked a top floor room with sea view and got a room on the middle floor with a view of mostly the car park. We could see a tiny part of the beach that had heaps of workers and tractors still renovating and it was a zone we could not enter. The walk along the whole beach was renovating areas. We also had a buffet lunch that was expensive and had listened to very loud jack hammers while eating because of renovations to the building. It would have been nice of them to discount us due to unpleasant renovations or at least tell us about it when booking our room. And the booking of the rooms is all a lie and total rip off for a sea view booking. The staff are not friendly compared to other places we stayed in Hong Kong.
Great Hotel. Great location. Sparkling clean. Great hospitality. Extremely well connected to city.

每一道菜都好好食😋
